{"tid":372182,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港癲佬力量：林浩基派心心比法子","createTime":"2017-08-24T07:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T06:19:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4f5ab43658c485e61ada92028ed1c349060ca4","tid":372182,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/21015847_1738250649537359_4822636159197025146_o.jpg?oh=a848f3c67144338ad76f2c5f2ec09e93&amp;oe=5A18CAC6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F21015847_1738250649537359_4822636159197025146_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da848f3c67144338ad76f2c5f2ec09e93%26oe%3D5A18CAC6&h=9326a004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社運界一啲都唔複雜，其實成個運作好簡單。好似老千達咁，擺幾件靚女出嚟護住個雞棚，原來又真係WORK架喎。<br />\n<br />\n早兩日，熱青城個法子，係咁易放張食腸嘅相出嚟；莫講話成班熱青城麻甩仔撲晒出嚟啦，就算連被熱青城清算過嘅，都敵唔過靚女攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n社運界太多一心諗住溝女食女嘅麻甩仔，冇眼睇。"},{"pid":"51dd6fe7faa68d6acd2e9873d304960a0d54a2c8","tid":372182,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"法子好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2607b4bc0475eb5922d4c92ec120c90e94d27a17","tid":372182,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法子好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你成世人未見過女人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f76287c28b2f0d294357f5090a3f3c10aeb848","tid":372182,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法子好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你成世人未見過女人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反熱狗還反熱狗<br />\n<br />\n法子係唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f